                    </div>
                    <p>My book Direitos Humanos das Mulheres e a Comissão Interamericana de Direitos Humanos,
                        (Saraiva,
                        2013) analyzes quantitative and qualitative data related to cases of women’s human rights
                        violations presented to the Inter-American Commission of Human Rights, identifying the
